	(453,1,'2012-11-06 21:30:30','2012-11-06 21:30:30','The Fianna is a nematode resistant variety with good processing qualities. It produces large oval shaped tubers, suitable for frying. It has smooth white skin, white flesh and shallow eyes. The Fianna is a medium late maturing variety, producing high yields of uniform attractive tubers. While principally used for french fries, this versatile potato is also good for the fresh market. The Fianna has a mealy cooking quality and medium dry matter content.','Fianna','The Fianna is a nematode resistant variety with good processing qualities. It produces large oval shaped tubers, suitable for frying. It has smooth white skin, white flesh and shallow eyes. The Fianna is a medium late maturing variety, producing high yields of uniform attractive tubers. While principally used for french fries, this versatile potato is also good for the fresh market. The Fianna has a mealy cooking quality and medium dry matter content.','publish','open','open','','fianna','','','2012-11-06 21:30:30','2012-11-06 21:30:30','',0,'http://premium-seed.com/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=453',0,'portfolio','',0),
